'''Gilitīro''' was a [[Falmari|Telerin]] [[Elf]] of [[Aman]] and the father of [[Celeborn]] according to one late version of the [[legendarium]].<ref name=PE23>{{PE|23b}}, p. 143</ref>

== Etymology ==
The name ''Gilitīro'' is in [[Telerin]], meaning "starwatcher".<ref name=PE23/>

Its [[Sindarin]] equivalent is '''''Gildír'''''.<ref name=PE23/>
